<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">I suppose we will end up finding a number of a=
nswers to that question. Will some ChatGPT-style large language model manag=
e to do some insider trading? Will it, like, ingest some corpus of data tha=
t includes inside information, and then use it to answer questions like =E2=
=80=9Cwhich stocks should I buy?=E2=80=9D Will some big company=E2=80=99s c=
orporate development department use the model to answer questions like =E2=
=80=9Cshould we buy Company X and what price should we pay for it,=E2=80=9D=
 and will the developers of the model use that information nefariously? Wil=
l the model itself become sentient, get a Robinhood account and use that in=
formation nefariously? Etc.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Or I mean will someone ask ChatGPT a question =
like =E2=80=9Cwhat companies are frauds,=E2=80=9D and ChatGPT will cheerful=
ly and confidently say =E2=80=9Coh Company Y is a total fraud, their revenu=
es are super inflated,=E2=80=9D and then people will short the stock, and t=
hen it will turn out that Company Y is fine and ChatGPT is just really good=
 at confidently making stuff up? Is that securities fraud? By whom? (Or: As=
k =E2=80=9Cwhat stocks are good,=E2=80=9D ChatGPT says =E2=80=9CCompany Z i=
s great, they have found a cure for cancer and their revenue will double,=
=E2=80=9D people buy the stock, it was all made up.) Will sell-side analyst=
s or journalists use ChatGPT to do their work, and will ChatGPT introduce m=
arket-moving factual mistakes?=C2=A0</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Lots of fun possibilities. But the most immedi=
ate way in which ChatGPT is going to be securities fraud is the usual =E2=
=80=9Ceverything is securities fraud=E2=80=9D way:</p>
<ol style=3D"list-style-type: decimal; padding-left: 40px; margin: 16px 0;"=
>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">ChatGPT is going to be disruptive to =
some number of businesses and industries.</li>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom=
: 5px;">Some companies will lose money because ChatGPT disrupts their busin=
ess.</li>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">This will be bad, for them, a=
nd their stocks will drop.</li>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">Every b=
ad thing that happens to a public company can be characterized as securitie=
s fraud: =E2=80=9CYou didn=E2=80=99t sufficiently warn us about the bad thi=
ng, so we bought the stock thinking it was good, but then the bad thing hap=
pened and the stock dropped, so we were defrauded.=E2=80=9D</li>
</ol>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">ChatGPT risk factors are <a href=3D"https://li=
nk.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/31366713.261431/aHR0cHM6Ly85ZmluLmNvbS9=
pbnNpZ2h0cy9jaGF0Z3B0LWlzLXRoZS1uZXctcmlzay1mYWN0b3ItYnV6endvcmQ/607f07ceef=
4b8524a319a23cB6d8831bb" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" tar=
get=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; b=
order-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style:=
 solid; background-color: #ccc;"> starting to be included in securities=C2=
=A0offering documents</a>, and the <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbu=
siness.com/click/31366713.261431/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9uZXdzL2=
FydGljbGVzLzIwMjMtMDUtMDIvY2hlZ2ctcGx1bmdlcy1hZnRlci13YXJuaW5nLXRoYXQtYWkta=
XMtdGhyZWF0ZW5pbmctaXRzLWJ1c2luZXNzP2NtcGlkPUJCRDA1MDMyM19NT05FWVNUVUZGJnV0=
bV9tZWRpdW09ZW1haWwmdXRtX3NvdXJjZT1uZXdzbGV0dGVyJnV0bV90ZXJtPTIzMDUwMyZ1dG1=
fY2FtcGFpZ249bW9uZXlzdHVmZg/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB6e12d1bc" itemprop=3D"=
StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #00000=
0; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-botto=
m-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">  ri=
sks are starting to be realized</a>:</p>
<blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Chegg Inc. plummeted 42% after warning that th=
e ChatGPT tool is threatening growth of its homework-help services, one of =
the most notable market reactions yet to signs that generative AI is upendi=
ng industries.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">The company, which offers online guidance for =
students taking tests and writing essays, also gave revenue and profit fore=
casts for the current quarter that fell well short of analysts=E2=80=99 est=
imates. Chegg makes much of its money from subscriptions, which start at $1=
5.95 a month, a revenue source that=E2=80=99s in peril if students see AI c=
hatbots as an alternative to paying.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">The impact of ChatGPT, an OpenAI tool that sur=
ged in popularity last year, began to be felt this spring, Chief Executive =
Officer Dan Rosensweig said in prepared remarks accompanying Chegg=E2=80=99=
s first-quarter earnings Monday.</p>
</blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">And I tell you what, when I see that a public =
company has=C2=A0announced bad news and its stock dropped, I look for the l=
awsuits. We are early yet =E2=80=94=C2=A0the stock dropped=C2=A0<em>yesterd=
ay=C2=A0</em>=E2=80=94=C2=A0but lawyers move fast; I have not yet seen any =
lawsuits filed, but at least <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness=
.com/click/31366713.261431/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuZ2xvYmVuZXdzd2lyZS5jb20vbmV3cy1y=
ZWxlYXNlLzIwMjMvMDUvMDMvMjY2MDQ3NC8wL2VuL0NIR0ctQWxlcnQtTW9uc2V5LUxhdy1GaXJ=
tLW9mLVdvaGwtRnJ1Y2h0ZXItTExQLUludmVzdGlnYXRpbmctQ2hlZ2ctSW5jLWZvci1Qb3Rlbn=
RpYWwtU2VjdXJpdGllcy1MYXctVmlvbGF0aW9ucy5odG1s/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cBbba=
fea4b" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" sty=
le=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width=
: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background=
-color: #ccc;"> two</a> law <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.=
com/click/31366713.261431/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYWJjMjcuY29tL2J1c2luZXNzL3ByZXNzL=
XJlbGVhc2VzL2dsb2JlbmV3c3dpcmUvODgzMDU2Mi9pbnZlc3RpZ2F0aW9uLWFsZXJ0LWtlc3Ns=
ZXItdG9wYXotbWVsdHplci1jaGVjay1sbHAtaXMtaW52ZXN0aWdhdGluZy1zZWN1cml0aWVzLWZ=
yYXVkLWNsYWltcy1vbi1iZWhhbGYtb2YtY2hlZ2ctaW5jLW55c2UtY2hnZy1pbnZlc3RvcnMv/6=
07f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB1b18dec4" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"items=
cope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !imp=
ortant; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bott=
om-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> firms</a> have announced =E2=80=
=9Cinvestigations=E2=80=9D of Chegg and are looking for clients.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">At this point the lawsuits seem a bit far-fetc=
hed: =E2=80=9CYou should have warned us months ago that artificial intellig=
ence would hurt your business=E2=80=9D is unfair given how quickly ChatGPT =
has exploded from nowhere to become a cultural and business phenomenon. But=
 now everyone is on notice! If you are not warning your shareholders now=C2=
=A0about how AI could hurt your business, and then it does hurt your busine=
ss, you=E2=80=99re gonna get sued.</p>
