<div id=3D"footnote-8" class=3D"footnote-content" style=3D"font-style: ital=
ic;">
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">[8] Another obvious and popular reason to be w=
orried about stock buybacks is that they are stock manipulation: Companies =
